The paper proposes a method for optimizing the parameters of deep neural networks using a generative adversarial network (GAN). This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are all relevant sub-categories. Additionally, the paper applies the proposed method to image classification tasks, which falls under the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the use of GANs for optimization also has applications in control systems, which is covered by the sub-category cs.SY (Systems and Control).
